            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Such a bad school environment. Teachers are blatantly partial towards the students. You will witness extreme favouritism in every classroom, this makes some students extremely cocky and arrogant. I remember my chemistry and english teacher saying I won't pass my board exam, guess what looks like you were wrong lmao. The Principal is a great guy to be honest but unfortunately that doesn't make up for everything else that is wrong. There were a few good souls though and I still remember them for their kindness they shown towards me.\n\nWords cannot describe my experience in this school but numbers can: 0/10",
          "publisher": {
